                <h1>Stop Bullying: Understand, Prevent, and Overcome</h1>
                <p>Bullying is a harmful behavior that can have lasting effects on individuals, both mentally and emotionally. It often occurs in schools or workplaces and can manifest as verbal, physical, or cyber abuse. Awareness and intervention are crucial in addressing bullying and creating a safe environment for everyone involved.</p>
